[size=4][b]What[/b][/size]

[size=3]Walk through NPCs instead of pushing them around. No more getting body-blocked by a townsfolk standing in a doorway.[/size]

[list]
[*][size=3]Covers every NPC in the game — townsfolk, refugees, Gerry, the donkey, your zombie workers, enemies, priests, merchants, the lot.[/size]
[*][size=3]Pathfinding and collision between NPCs is untouched — they still navigate around each other and the world normally. Only your collision with them is removed.[/size]
[*][size=3]Applies immediately on install. No unlocks, no setup.[/size]
[/list]

[size=4][b]Other mods of mine you might like[/b][/size]

[list]
[*][size=3][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/graveyardkeeper/mods/55]Misc. Bits and Bobs[/url] — includes a player movement speed multiplier and an "evict church visitors" button for when the congregation won't leave.[/size]
[*][size=3][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/graveyardkeeper/mods/61]Beam Me Up Gerry[/url] — fast-travel to skip crowded routes entirely.[/size]
[*][size=3][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/graveyardkeeper/mods/60]I Build Where I Want[/url] — build paths and structures without zone restrictions.[/size]
[/list]

[size=4][b]Configuration[/b][/size]

[size=3]If you installed the required [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/graveyardkeeper/mods/79]Graveyard Keeper BepInEx 5 Pack[/url] and this mod is configurable, press F1 in-game to open the config interface.[/size]

[size=4][b]Requirements[/b][/size]

[list]
[*][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/graveyardkeeper/mods/79][size=3]Graveyard Keeper BepInEx 5 Pack at Graveyard Keeper Nexus - Mods and community (nexusmods.com)[/size][/url]
[/list]
[size=4][b]Installation[/b][/size]

[size=3]Installation using Vortex is the recommended installation method. If you wish to install manually, extract the contents of the mod archive into:

[code]...&#92;steamapps&#92;common&#92;Graveyard Keeper&#92;BepInEx[/code][/size]

